reviewText: I bought 'Bikini Warriors' thinking I would get to see the hot lady on the cover  (Kylee Nash) duking it out with other women behind bars. Unfortunately the female fight club part of the plot never develops.  Instead it's seven sex scenes strung together by humorous dialogue and bad acting. Joslyn James character Cindy has sex with a cop, a jail guard, her lawyer, a crimeboss, and last but not least, her fight club rival Sascha played by Kylee Nash. Kylee Nash also has sex with the cop and crimeboss. I was disappointed in the lack of catfights but was impressed by how hot Kylee & Joslyn are.

It's a ripoff.
